text.tspan: CHOOSE ONE OF THE 4 BUTTONS WITH MOUSE CLICK
In this task, you play a "gambling" game. You need to choose one
of 4 buttons (A, B, C, or D) with the mouse.
Each time, you can win some money, but you may sometimes
also have to pay a fee to the bank. After each trial, you need to
collect your money, which will adjust your pot of money.
You start with a loan of $2000.
There are 100 trials (taking 5 minutes or so).
Go on until it stops and see how much you can make
Press space bar to start. Good luck!
Click here to collect (and/or pay fee)
